---
// 3. Compare — "the usual" vs Lingo7 Realty (rows reveal on scroll).
---
<section class="compare" id="why">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section__title" data-i18n="compare.title"><strong class="hero__hl">Study in your own language</strong> and pass with confidence in&nbsp;English.</h2>
    <p class="section__subtitle" data-i18n="compare.subtitle"><strong class="hero__hl">You grasp the meaning right away</strong>, while an adaptive trainer drills exam questions until they're&nbsp;second nature.</p>
    <div class="compare__list">

      <div class="compare__row">
        <div class="compare__old">
          <span class="compare__label compare__label--old" data-i18n="compare.row1.old-label">❌ The usual</span>
          <strong data-i18n="compare.row1.old-title">Everything is in English only</strong>
          <p data-i18n="compare.row1.old-text">Textbook, terminology, questions, answer explanations — your energy goes into the language instead of the material.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="compare__arrow">→</div>
        <div class="compare__new">
          <span class="compare__label compare__label--new" data-i18n="compare.row1.new-label">✅ Lingo7 Realty</span>
          <strong data-i18n="compare.row1.new-title">Built-in parallel translation</strong>
          <p data-i18n="compare.row1.new-text">Every bit of content comes with a translation into your language. You get the meaning instantly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="compare__row">
        <div class="compare__old">
          <span class="compare__label compare__label--old" data-i18n="compare.row2.old-label">❌ The usual</span>
          <strong data-i18n="compare.row2.old-title">Hundreds of terms and questions — impossible to keep in your head</strong>
          <p data-i18n="compare.row2.old-text">Cramming with no system is a treadmill: you learn one thing and forget another.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="compare__arrow">→</div>
        <div class="compare__new">
          <span class="compare__label compare__label--new" data-i18n="compare.row2.new-label">✅ Lingo7 Realty</span>
          <strong data-i18n="compare.row2.new-title">Built-in spaced repetition</strong>
          <p data-i18n="compare.row2.new-text">Every saved term and question comes back right as you start to forget — a scientifically proven way to make it stick.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="compare__row">
        <div class="compare__old">
          <span class="compare__label compare__label--old" data-i18n="compare.row3.old-label">❌ The usual</span>
          <strong data-i18n="compare.row3.old-title">You stumble on every word you don't know</strong>
          <p data-i18n="compare.row3.old-text">You stop, lose your train of thought — and your progress slows down.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="compare__arrow">→</div>
        <div class="compare__new">
          <span class="compare__label compare__label--new" data-i18n="compare.row3.new-label">✅ Lingo7 Realty</span>
          <strong data-i18n="compare.row3.new-title">One loop: question → translation → review</strong>
          <p data-i18n="compare.row3.new-text">It all happens in one place — language stops getting in the way: you stay focused and learn faster.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
